{"tid":647314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(張敬軒唔該入一入嚟)買張敬軒飛比呀媽睇 變左用底褲換？","createTime":"2018-04-29T17:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T07:47:40.000Z","uid":117996,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4b99ace86f87fb58a8fb3e621ee7b429389cbc","tid":647314,"uid":117996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T17:46:01.000Z","msg":"話說頭先女朋友send左幾張圖比我睇<br />\n睇到眼火爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前排張敬軒演唱會公開發售 我陪左女朋友訓街一齊買<br />\n結果排我哋前邊果兩個人買埋最後嘅飛<br />\n我地買唔到 佢好唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為好想同佢媽睇<br />\n之後我同女朋友就不斷睇下有冇人放飛<br />\n佢今日就收到以下呢位 小佛系 既tg訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/013134_71c4e34911c5f992a7292bbfc94612c2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F013134_71c4e34911c5f992a7292bbfc94612c2.png&h=30f71ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/013135_3e9601df9c38b5047bb2679405de4eb8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F013135_3e9601df9c38b5047bb2679405de4eb8.png&h=b0bfd871&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/013139_83900c6ede8b794567419d88ca1b0e3c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F013139_83900c6ede8b794567419d88ca1b0e3c.png&h=b09b3993&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/013140_1d2845bf5f3aa6a5de14f782d1b97da7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F013140_1d2845bf5f3aa6a5de14f782d1b97da7.png&h=ae641715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實睇到呢到 我同女朋友講唔好交換 呢個人好有問題 <br />\n之後呢個小佛系仲前言不對後語 又話放380票價既飛<br />\n但張敬軒演唱會只有280 480 780飛<br />\n佢係當人on9定自己on9？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/013527_e0dba45bb738b4dde8995701bba0d4e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F013527_e0dba45bb738b4dde8995701bba0d4e8.png&h=ab29ebef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/013528_8a325d5a1c776b8c2883c47a4a844f85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F013528_8a325d5a1c776b8c2883c47a4a844f85.png&h=323920ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/014306_b560268f20764e8084ed658f18b03d81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F014306_b560268f20764e8084ed658f18b03d81.png&h=71a3d876&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/013532_e12330ed8b3ea1e047c8c853cfea6466.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F013532_e12330ed8b3ea1e047c8c853cfea6466.png&h=9930f4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後仲send左張超級矇既飛黎比我女朋友睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉想睇個演唱會都要用底褲交換<br />\n點解香港會咁？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 其實我覺得一定會有人為左睇演唱會而出賣自己<br />\n希望各位小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講開又講 其實我都好想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n大家黎評下理<br />\n香港人依家睇個演唱會一係訓幾晚街 一係就食黃牛價 再唔係就比底褲人<br />\n咩世界？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次排黃子華都係訓街先好彩買到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c406f7fb2cc4c11fc5e2a917877a11a794f25f4","tid":647314,"uid":99568,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T17:47:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WFC</span>支那軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1caef88684b3ccafba56d19add8ca0182569232","tid":647314,"uid":109602,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T17:48:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fbb0f40c7d24560216d4601de81fc93b48cb7c8","tid":647314,"uid":117901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"你爆左你女朋友個名出黎.."},{"pid":"88c55584edbf896b5deb5bf91d4fa561d755657a","tid":647314,"uid":96,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fbb0f40c7d24560216d4601de81fc93b48cb7c8","tid":647314,"uid":117901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"你爆左你女朋友個名出黎.."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"waiting<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講咁耐都唔見你條女有話拒絕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1bda2e6763a7bec2b912944f07101b829aa144","tid":647314,"uid":117996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T17:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說頭先女朋友send左幾張圖比我睇<br />\n睇到眼火爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前排張敬軒演唱會公開發售 我陪左女朋友訓街一齊買<br />\n結果排我哋前邊果兩個人買埋最後嘅飛<br />\n我地買唔到 佢好唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為好想同佢媽